                    "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"21\" data-pf2-traits=\"poison\" data-pf2-label=\"Mandragora Venom DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span>;</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 rounds;</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> [[/r 1d6 #poison]] poison damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} (1 round);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> [[/r 1d6 #poison]] poison damage, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Confused]{Confused}, and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} (1 round);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> [[/r 2d6 #poison]] poison damage, confused, and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} (1 round)</p>"
